('services', '📊 Lead generation (Apollo)', 'Verified B2B leads pulled from Apollo. Fixed pricing: 5,000 leads = $20 total; 10,000 leads = $35 total. Delivered as CSV within 24 hours. Fields include name, role, company, email, LinkedIn, website.', 10),
