('faq', 'How fresh is the data?', 'All leads are verified within the last 30 days before delivery. Emails run through a validator; bounced rows are replaced free.', 10),
('faq', 'What formats do you deliver?', 'CSV by default. XLSX or Google Sheets on request — no extra charge.', 20),
('faq', 'Can I get a free sample?', 'Yes — every list ships with a free 10-row sample on request before payment. Tap "Talk to a human" to request one.', 30),
('faq', 'What countries do you cover?', 'Global coverage. Strongest in USA, Canada, UK, EU, Australia. Ask for a specific country and we will confirm volume.', 40),
('faq', 'What is your bounce guarantee?', 'Under 5% bounce rate guaranteed. If a delivery exceeds that, we replace bounced rows free within 7 days.', 50),
('faq', 'How long does delivery take?', 'Prebuilt lists: instant download after payment. Apollo custom lists: within 24 hours. Manual research: 2–5 business days.', 60),
