('faq', 'How do payments work?', 'We accept card (Stripe), PayPal, and crypto. Invoice on request for orders over $200.', 80),
('faq', 'Can I resell the data?', 'No — data is licensed for your own outbound only. Ask about reseller/enterprise licenses if needed.', 90),
('faq', 'Is the data GDPR / CCPA compliant?', 'Yes — sourced from publicly available business records. We include an opt-out header field in every delivery.', 100),

